Design decisions:
- **`value`/`onValueChange`/`defaultValue`**: This mirrors the SidebarProvider pattern at `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775504564704-dwzo3r/apps/v4/registry/new-york-v4/ui/sidebar.tsx` lines 56-80 for controlled/uncontrolled usage. The value is a numeric step index (1-based).
